metadata.name: 01 Lust
metadata.description:
We are very weak creatures, easily crushed, and scattered. One of our weaknesses is about love. Humans are even ready to sacrifice anything to satisfy their lust for love. We often want virtual touch to physical touch on our mate, just to make our hearts calm, to sexual touch that reconciles our hearts. And what we feel when nothing gets fulfilled is really broken and torn apart.

This token has been enhanced using Augmented Reality, and you will find it moving on your camera. Also find hidden objects in this token, using the Artilive App from your device.
